name: AI Data Dashboard
description:
A concept for an AI Dashboard with 3 examples of interfaces.


Dark mode

For "darkers", choose this configuration if you like fluor lights and feel like a hacker. Also if you want to save your eyes during years.


Default mode

This is a default color palette with the brand colors. But you can edit main color in Components page.


Lite mode

If you are a border and plane style lover this is your option. Just the same but with a minimal touch.


Enjoy!
